EN LA MADRUGADA SE FUE won the Latin Grammy Award for Best Grupero Performance.

EN LA MADRUGADA SE FUE won the Billboard Latin Music Award for Regional Mexican Album of the Year by a Male Group.


After taking a solo vacation to Playa this past summer, I heard the most beautiful song and asked the waiter the name of it and the group. Te Hice Mal...Los Temerarios scribbled on a napkin. The next day I walked to every music store in town until I found it...and I listened to this CD my entire trip. By the end of the trip I had memorized the words to Te Hice Mal, even though I know little Spanish. I&#039;m now in love with Spanish music and taking Spanish lessons. When I&#039;m down, I simply put on my music and I&#039;m on the beach in Playa again. Can&#039;t wait to go back, but for now...I have these guys.
